query:
SELECT SQL_NO_CACHE p.id, p.id_paciente, p.nome, p.cpf, p.telefone, p.status_caso
FROM pacientes p
WHERE p.tenant_id = 1 AND p.deleted_at IS NULL
ORDER BY p.nome ASC
LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0;
